---
import GuideLayout from "../../layouts/GuideLayout.astro";

const title = "SSM Parameter Store pricing: what to model (advanced params + API calls)";
const description =
  "A practical Parameter Store pricing checklist: standard vs advanced parameters, API call volume, and the common patterns that create request-driven cost spikes.";
---
<GuideLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonicalPath="/guides/aws-ssm-parameter-store-pricing"
  lastUpdated="2026-01-22"
  faqs={[
    {
      q: "What typically drives Parameter Store cost?",
      a: "API call volume. Advanced parameter count can add a steady baseline, but high-frequency GetParameter calls often dominate total spend.",
    },
    {
      q: "Why do costs spike in Kubernetes or serverless?",
      a: "Because frequent cold starts or pod churn can trigger many parameter fetches. If each instance fetches multiple parameters, the request volume scales quickly.",
    },
  ]}
>
  <p>
    Parameter Store cost is often a mix of <strong>advanced parameter-month</strong> charges plus <strong>API request</strong>
    charges. The main risk is request-driven spend from chatty application patterns.
  </p>

  <h2>What to model</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Standard vs advanced parameters</strong>: advanced parameters often have a monthly per-parameter charge
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>API calls/month</strong>: GetParameter(s), PutParameter, List*, and related calls
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Caller patterns</strong>: per-request fetches vs per-startup fetches
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>A fast estimate</h2>
  <p class="muted">
    Use <a href="/calculators/aws-ssm-parameter-store-cost-calculator/">AWS SSM Parameter Store Cost Calculator</a> to model
    advanced parameters + API calls with your effective pricing.
  </p>

  <h2>Validation checklist</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Confirm how often applications fetch parameters (per request vs per startup).</li>
    <li>Estimate calls/month from instance count and fetch frequency; validate with a real week of usage.</li>
    <li>Watch for spike drivers: pod churn, cold starts, and retry loops.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Related tools</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a class="btn" href="/calculators/aws-ssm-parameter-store-cost-calculator/">Parameter Store cost</a>
    <a class="btn" href="/guides/request-based-pricing/">Request-based pricing</a>
    <a class="btn" href="/guides/cloud-cost-estimation-checklist/">Cost checklist</a>
  </div>
</GuideLayout>
